---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SAVOY Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa</title>
    
    <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js" is:inline></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#050505] text-[#e0e0e0] antialiased selection:bg-white selection:text-black overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="absolute w-full z-50 top-0 px-8 py-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-12 text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            <a href="/camere" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-300">Residenze</a>
            <a href="/spa" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-300">Thermae</a>
            <a href="/ristorante" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-300">Gusto</a>
        </div>
        <a href="#booking" class="text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border border-white/50 px-6 py-2 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            Booking
        </a>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center overflow-hidden text-center px-4">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540541338287-41700207dee6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80" alt="Savoy Dark" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 scale-105" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-black/20 to-[#050505]"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 mt-16">
            <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl text-white font-light tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 drop-shadow-2xl" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                Savoy<span class="text-[#d4af37]">.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm md:text-xl tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-light" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa
            </p>
            <div class="w-px h-24 bg-white/30 mx-auto mt-12"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="sticky top-32 h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611892440504-42a792e24d32?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Dettaglio Architettura" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-1000">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center pt-20 md:pt-0">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">01. L'Ospitalità</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                La Nuova <br> <i>Dimensione</i>.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-base font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-md" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>Un rifugio di design sospeso tra la sabbia di Bibione e le acque termali. Camere ampie, luminose e pensate per offrirti il massimo del comfort e della privacy.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/camere" class="text-white text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Esplora le Stanze <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-20">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-[60vh] md:h-[80vh]">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Thermal Spa" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-1000">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">02. Il Benessere</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Acque</i> <br> Curative.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-base font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-md" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>Un corridoio segreto ti separa dal mondo. In accappatoio, dalla tua suite, raggiungi direttamente e in totale privacy le sorgenti di Bibione Thermae.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/spa" class="text-white text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Scopri i Trattamenti <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative h-[80vh] w-full flex items-center mt-20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80" alt="Ristorante" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 w-full text-center px-4">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">03. Il Gusto</p>
            <h2 class="text-7xl md:text-[8vw] text-white font-light leading-none mb-8" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                Duca <i>d'Aosta</i>
            </h2>
            <a href="/ristorante" class="mt-4 inline-block text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                Scopri il Menù
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-24">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">I Nostri Servizi</p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white font-light" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Attenzioni</i> Esclusive.
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-16 gap-x-8 text-center" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🏖️</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Spiaggia Privata</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Settore VIP Riservato</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🧖‍♀️</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Tunnel Termale</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Accesso Diretto Spa</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🚗</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Garage Coperto</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Colonnine Elettriche</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🚲</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Noleggio Bici</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Esplora Bibione</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🐕</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Pet Friendly</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Servizi per Animali</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🏊‍♂️</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Piscina Esterne</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Solarium & Lounge</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">🥂</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Lounge Bar</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Cocktail & Cantina</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group">
                <span class="text-3xl block mb-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all">📶</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Wi-Fi Veloce</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Connessione Ovunque</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 bg-[#050505] border-t border-white/10 text-center flex justify-between px-8">
        <p class="text-[#555] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            © 2026 Savoy Beach Hotel.
        </p>
        <a href="/admin/" class="text-[#555] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase hover:text-white transition-colors" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            Admin
        </a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>